{"tid":2311617,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新書台灣奪獎 馬嶽：榮歸港人","createTime":"2020-12-04T08:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T08:17:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7a8b2e2c3670d5400df7cbaaf31d20d68a36a7","tid":2311617,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/6GRWVQBB3ZC67ERBO3PJ4I3IQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2F6GRWVQBB3ZC67ERBO3PJ4I3IQY%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=5d939b00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2F6GRWVQBB3ZC67ERBO3PJ4I3IQY%2F&h=5e395bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/6GRWVQBB3ZC67ERBO3PJ4I3IQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新書台灣奪獎 馬嶽：榮歸港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TM5YQNtgbt2rYWpshn8oyIR-f7U=/720x488/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YGFB6DWNCVAMVFJ5LI7NSPQQCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTM5YQNtgbt2rYWpshn8oyIR-f7U%3D%2F720x488%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYGFB6DWNCVAMVFJ5LI7NSPQQCY.jpg&h=98d7bc30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬嶽（左圖）新書《反抗的共同體》（右圖）奪得台灣Openbook年度中文創作獎。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中抗爭至今超過一年，文字紀錄成運動重要印記，台灣華文出版界一年一度「2020 Openbook好書獎」昨揭曉得獎名單，中大政治與行政學系副教授馬嶽以《反抗的共同體：2019香港反送中運動》獲得年度中文創作獎，評審認為作者精闢剖析反送中前因後果。馬嶽在獲獎感言提到，「這本書能得到的所有榮耀，自然都應該是屬於2019年那些展現反抗精神的香港人的，我只是一個記錄者而已。」<br />\n<br />\nOpenbook好書獎由台灣書評網站Openbook閱讀誌主辦，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評審：國安法下書寫需勇氣<br />\n<br />\n馬嶽以《反抗的共同體》榮獲年度中文創作，全書400頁，共20萬字，序言一句：「我希望這本書可以幫很多人記着2019年在香港發生的事。」全書共13章，從雨傘運動後的局勢，反送中抗爭的前因後果、6月起抗爭的多次轉折，不合作運動、到末章的運動影響。本報昨聯絡馬嶽但未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n評審認為，該書是目前中文世界中，由。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/Openbook閱讀誌官網"},{"pid":"0385a14b8c3b29f5233beeb94fed3aa652b19a8d","tid":2311617,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}